    <title>解决当 使用 hexo d 命令 显示 ERROR Deployer not found: git 问题</title>
    <url>/2020/09/30/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%BD%93-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-hexo-d-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4-%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git-%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>出现该问题是因为没有安装对应部署，执行下面命令即可</p>
<p><code>npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</code></p>
